{"url": "https://aplus.com/a/gabourey-sidibe-responds-instagram-troll-prayer?no_monetization=true", "text": "\"I'm not sure why you're so mad and I don't need to know why, Betty,\" the 34-year-old started out. \"What I do know is that you are clearly suffering and you're probably reaching out in nastiness in order to get some attention and you've got mine.\n\n\"You have my attention and my concern and now my hand extended to you in prayer that your situation and your heart is healed,\" Sidibe added, continuing the \"bless your heart\"-like magnum opus. \"I don't have to know your needs to ask the Lord to provide those needs to you. May you receive this prayer in love and my God's peace and guidance fall on you and life and keep you in love.\"\n\nAs of publication, it appears @bettypowell47 has not replied to Sidibe's lengthy response. In fact, it appears the user has deleted their mean-spirited comments entirely.", "images": ["http://b.scorecardresearch.com/p?c1=2&c2=18288969&cv=2.0&cj=1", "https://images5.aplus.com/380x220/uc-up/a5596062-cae2-42d4-8bb0-bbfa62f363db/a5596062-cae2-42d4-8bb0-bbfa62f363db.crop_4150x2178_0,236.resize_1200x630.format_jpeg.inline_yes.jpg", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/mobile/nav/youtube-ff92d450ad69e9329c56ea47f91fdd20d45b35ae5206a0a2f1b4412809dc2154.png", "https://images5.aplus.com/380x220/uc-up/2dbd18ab-2b1b-4b6b-93ff-62e469250c59/2dbd18ab-2b1b-4b6b-93ff-62e469250c59.crop_5184x2722_0,367.resize_1200x630.format_jpeg.inline_yes.jpg", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/aplus-logo-bd818654faabbd94d892b2eacfd9f6d9bf1c3a326371b4ad6e0b37adb1ba994d.png", "https://images5.aplus.com/380x220/uc-up/e86c5ca8-fd5e-44b1-bcf0-d8e462e8d0a4/e86c5ca8-fd5e-44b1-bcf0-d8e462e8d0a4.crop_4544x2386_0,265.resize_1200x630.format_jpeg.inline_yes.jpg", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/aplus_logo_white-6141173fb2f35a62f94cfff70b3b3c022691defb4e6aa50bae3ad6e1460fdb9d.png", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/mobile/nav/tumblr-e9ac0073ef34f889ea80041cffc785d83944016126296ba842